msgstr "控制此外掛相對於其他折扣外掛套用折扣的時機。"

msgid "Controls how multiple applicable rules interact. \"Priority\" uses the priority number set in each rule. \"Highest/Lowest\" calculates and applies the best discount. \"Stack All\" combines all discounts."
